        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 5h13a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H9l-4 3v-3H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1z"/></svg>
        Get a Free Quote
      </a>
